    <p>PS: If you cannot send a video to this donor because of travel or for any reason, no worries, please forward this email to Matthew so he can re-assign :)</p>
    <p>Gratitude Video Guidelines:</p>
    <p>- Keep it short. 30secs-1min is fine.</p>
    <p>- Start by waving and saying their name ("Hi Susanâ€¦")</p>
    <p>- You can be mobile, really anywhere. No problem.</p>
    <p>- This video should not look or feel "produced" or "perfect." Just be yourself.</p>
    <p>- <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q9ioBVyjJgw"> See here for an example.</a></p>
